title: 38. We Can Do Hard Things: An Impromptu Quarantine Pep Talk With Tess.
description:
Hi treatment Roomies, Tess here! No fancy skin talk or impressive guests in this one... Just a little impromptu pep talk in this episode. I hope you'r edoing well, and if you're not, I hope this episode perks you up a bit and helps get you back on track. In this episode I'm discussing 5 motivational quotes that have been lifting me up lately in quarantine!

Lauren's Instagram: @laurens.esthetics + Lauren's Blog www.lauren-kruger.com

Tess' Instagram @myestytessa.dermaplus + Tess' YouTube: Tess Zolly

Music by LiQwYd
